				</div>
				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="dablink">For Greek as used in particular eras, see <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ancient_Greek" title="Ancient Greek">Ancient Greek</a>, <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Koine_Greek" title="Koine Greek">Koine Greek</a>, and <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Modern_Greek" title="Modern Greek">Modern Greek</a>.</div>
