<li><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ancient_Greek" title="Ancient Greek">Ancient Greek</a> (c. 800–300 BC)</li>
<li><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Koine_Greek" title="Koine Greek">Koine Greek</a> (c. 300 BC–AD 330)</li>
<li><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Medieval_Greek" title="Medieval Greek">Medieval Greek</a> (c. 330–1453)</li>
<li><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Modern_Greek" title="Modern Greek">Modern Greek</a> (since 1453)</li>
